Class FriendsList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.swapmyride.FriendsList

  • public class FriendsList
extends java.lang.Object
    FriendsList is an object that holds a series of usernames which are indicated to be friends of a certain user, and provides an easy way to access and mutate this data
